<br>
Well, eventually the desire to not miss the GM event dragged me out of my stupor and I wander over to my system to see &quot;zone down, we have moved you to a safe place&quot;.  Yeah, a safe place in a level 30+ zone and I'm level 14.<br>
<br>
It was an interesting evening, trying to find the teleport spires dodging giants and wyrms and other nasty beasties.  <br>
<br>
Many thanks to Wuru and Rondo who helped a lowly bard get through the ordeal and return to the far more relative safety of the Warrens.  On the positive side, I did get my rings and one earring (still have a free ear) and upgraded my weapon.  Still can't proc the thing but I never do seem to hold onto weapons long enough for them to proc.  <br>
<br>
Ktiani <br>
Singer of songs and teller of tales<br>
<br>
P.S.  Next time I'll remember to ask what cycle the portal is on before I take a nap.<br>
